Assalamu Alaikum! It seems like you want to create a simple game using HTML and run it on CodePen.io. Here's a basic example of how you can create a simple game using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript:

**HTML Code:**
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>My Simple Game</title>
  <style>
    /* Add some basic styling to our game */
    body {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
    }
    #game-container {
      width: 400px;
      height: 400px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="game-container">
    <!-- Our game will go here -->
    <h1>My Simple Game</h1>
    <button id="start-button">Start Game</button>
    <div id="game-area"></div>
  </div>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
```
**JavaScript Code (in script.js file):**
```javascript
const startButton = document.getElementById('start-button');
const gameArea = document.getElementById('game-area');

startButton.addEventListener('click', startGame);

function startGame() {
  // Initialize the game
  gameArea.innerHTML = '';
  let score = 0;

  // Create a simple game loop
  setInterval(() => {
    // Generate a random number between 1 and 10
    const randomNumber = Math.floor(Math.random() * 10) + 1;

    // Create a new element to display the number
    const numberElement = document.createElement('div');
    numberElement.textContent = randomNumber;
    gameArea.appendChild(numberElement);

    // Update the score
    score += randomNumber;
    document.getElementById('score').textContent = `Score: ${score}`;
  }, 1000); // Run the game loop every 1 second
}
```
**How to Run the Game on CodePen:**

1. Create a new Pen on CodePen.io.
2. Copy the HTML code and paste it into the HTML section of your Pen.
3. Create a new file by clicking the "+" icon next to the HTML section, and name it "script.js".
4. Copy the JavaScript code and paste it into the script.js file.
5. Click the "Save" button to save your Pen.
6. Click the "Run" button to run the game.

Note: This is a very basic example, and you can improve it by adding more features, styling, and functionality.
